string.name: message
string.value: As I hear the loud cry of the Nine Spirit's Baby Dragon, a mystical power is rising within me!

Hey, did you manage to find the antidote...? You weren't able to get one from the Sage Cat...? Isn't that obvious? If he was to give you the antidote that easily, then he wouldn't have poisoned me in the first place... Cough cough!
There's no other way now. You'll need to defeat #rSage Cat#k and obtain the #bAntidote Marble#k! I truly believe... (gasping for air)... you... are... capable of...doing it...good luck.

Hello, dear guest, welcome. Is there something I can get for you? How about a cup of #t4031833#? Please let me know if there is anything I can help you with. My Master wishes to ensure that everyone has a wonderful time at the party.

Oh I almost forgot. The Master has prepared a special gift for all our guests. Whomever will bring back some sweet #t2022255# will receive a #b#t1002699##k, just right for celebrating the Halloween season! Would you like to participate in the #bGathering of #t2022255##k activities?

If you will bring back #b50 #t2022255#s#k left over from making Jack-o'-Lanterns, I will give you a cute little #b#t1002699##k in return. You have to make a Jack-o'-Lantern to say that you've properly celebrated Halloween!
If you would like to make a Jack-o'-Lantern, please talk to me and I will let you know where to go to make one. I hope you are enjoying yourself at the party...
Seems that you have no interest in collecting #t2022255#. Nothing I can do about that. Hope you're enjoying the party.

I know who you are. You were born a Pirate a long time ago aboard the mighty vessel known as the Nautilus. You established your presence and power at the land of the snow, and...I also bestowed you of a new name worthy of a great Pirate...

Now that you have reached the apex as a Pirate, I'll introduce to you a new companion. Countless Pirates, from Ms.Behave to Loosetooth Pete, strived for it, but couldn't get it, and now you have the opportunity to get it... What do you think...do you want #t1902002#?
If you are ready to initiate a powerful friendship, then let me know.
I don't think you are ready. No one in Maple can defeat you, so why fear the change? As the undisputed master of the sea, one who feels at home amongst the waves, this should seem enticing to you...
